HEADWORD: Symphonious
<hw>Sym*pho"ni*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Symphony</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Agreeing in sound; accordant;
